title: Last winless NFL team?
description:
This market will resolve according to the team that remains without a single win the longest during the 2025–26 NFL regular season.

Ties do not count as wins.

If multiple teams earn their first win in games scheduled at the same time on the same day, while being the last remaining winless teams, the market will resolve according to the order in which the games actually end.

If the games end at the exact same time or if multiple teams remain winless through the end of the regular season, the market will resolve to the team whose listed name comes first alphabetically.

The resolution source for this market will be the National Football League (NFL.com).

This market will resolve to "Up" if the Ethereum price at the end of the time range specified in the title is greater than or equal to the price at the beginning of that range. Otherwise, it will resolve to "Down".
The resolution source for this market is information from Chainlink, specifically the ETH/USD data stream available at https://data.chain.link/streams/eth-usd.
Please note that this market is about the price according to Chainlink data stream ETH/USD, not according to other sources or spot markets.
